<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE BELIEVER'S SECURITY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thilpha i muh bang uh,
 Kuoma'n a mu thei puou;
 I Pau gam thil ahi,
 Khawvelte muh phakloh.
 Gibang ei khen thei um puo'n a,
 Pathien hehpihna apat chun.

[V2]
 2. A thukzie gentheih loh,
 A sanzie gentheih loh;
 Lungsietna lienpen hih,
 A man simsen guolloh.
 Nanghaw van a mithiengte-haw'n,
 A lopi zie nei hilh thei u'm

[V3]
 3. Khawvel bei ding eita'i,
 A nunkhaw nuom haw tawh;
 A vanglaini haw hi,
 Pakbang in tuoi in a.
 Ka Lalpa'n tuoini nei puo'n a,
 Linglukhuk in tuomvel mahleh.

[V4]
 4. Khawvel sesum pha leh,
 Go thilpha haw cheng hih;
 A hawihna haw cheng hi,
 Pakbang in tuoi in a.
 Khawvel pakbang tuoi ding sang in,
 Ka Lalpa hih a hawih ka sa'i.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>20</hymn_number>
</song>